data.description: Welcome to your new home.  You will love the floor plan w/ample living space for all.  You are greeted w/a sweet front porch   to enjoy your morning coffee and a nice living/flex room.  Huge great room boasting an inviting gas fireplace & copious windows to add sunlight. Charming kitchen with abundant stained pine cabinets, granite counters, hardwood floors & comfortable island.  Rest easy in this huge king size bedroom complete w/ double vanity, step in shower, soaker tub, and walk in shower.  3 additional bedrooms complete this home.  Large fenced backyard with oversized patio for all your entertaining needs.  Large 3 bay garage and RV Parking Potential.  Lets turn this house into your HOME.
